<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Email Tasdiqlash</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #2d3436;
        }

        .container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h2 {
            color: #2d3436;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .code {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .email-highlight {
            color: #764ba2;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        p {
            margin: 16px 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Email Tasdiqlash</h2>
        </div>

        <p>Assalomu alaykum!</p>

        <p>
            Quyidagi kodni email manzilingizni tasdiqlash uchun ishlatishingiz mumkin
            (<span class="email-highlight">
                <%= email %>
            </span>):
        </p>

        <div class="code">
            <%= confirmationCode %>
        </div>

        <p>Ushbu kod 30 daqiqa ichida yaroqsiz bo'ladi.</p>

        <p>
            Agar siz ushbu tasdiqlash kodini so'ramagan bo'lsangiz, iltimos, bu xabarni e'tiborsiz qoldiring.
        </p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Hurmat bilan,<br />Wordsuz.uz</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>